<li>Faminepulse created the original mp3.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1525392630" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;">Decibelles</a></span> (AKA me) improved the mp3 and modified it in a few ways, as well as wrote the other 10% of it and helped with a joke or two.</li>
</ul>
<p>So this is a three-way co-author deal.</p>
<p>I think the SCP Wiki is ready for this again. Especially since I changed it a bit since the last time.</p>
<p>Translations:</p>
